            "children": {
              "true": [
                {
                  "command": "EVENT_TEXT",
                  "args": {
                    "text": [
                      "Yeah? All my other\noptions suck. I'm too old\nfor foster care and I\nwouldn't want to go into\n that hell system anyway.",
                      "Rent costs arm and a leg\nand have you SEEN how\nthe homeless get \ntreated? Awful."
                    ],
                    "avatarId": ""
                  },
                  "id": "3e85a34b-0627-4a0a-b052-c9c46dd89002"
                }
              ],
              "false": [
                {
                  "command": "EVENT_TEXT",
                  "args": {
                    "text": [
                      "I really don't think that\nwill help. You'll just make\nthings worse for me. I\ndon't want to prosecute."
                    ],
                    "avatarId": ""
                  },
                  "id": "6c7317ff-0fb9-4086-ad26-a0eb618bd092"
                }
              ]
            },
            "id": "72db9491-64df-40a3-8e5d-9ae2766ef9e2"
          }
        ],
        "false": [
          {
            "id": "1063f8a8-90b7-4126-b6e4-1daf7c359c87",
            "command": "EVENT_TEXT",
            "args": {
              "text": [
                "Are you here about my\ncomplaints?",
                "Number one: that vile\nsquirrel is chewing holes",
                "in my house all through\nthe night.",
                "Number two: My mom\nwon't let me back in the",
                "house. I'm gonna freeze!"
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "7a86534c-dd9f-4005-b2e7-c880ea3f9014",
